  "prompt": "Which are the top architects in pune?",
  "response": "Pune has a vibrant architectural scene with several renowned architects and firms known for their innovative designs and sustainable practices. While the list can be subjective and based on various criteria such as project quality, reputation, and client satisfaction, some of the well-regarded architects and firms in Pune include:\n\n1. **Vilas Shinde Architects** - Known for their residential and commercial projects, they focus on modern architecture while integrating traditional elements.\n\n2. **Mithun S. Rane Architects** - Specializing in contemporary and sustainable architecture, they have a strong portfolio in both residential and institutional projects.\n\n3. **Sanjay Puri Architects** - A nationally recognized firm with a focus on sustainable and innovative designs, they have completed several notable projects across India, including in Pune.\n\n4. **Karan Grover & Associates** - Known for their environmentally conscious designs, they have worked on numerous residential, commercial, and institutional projects.\n\n5. **Studio Lotus** - While based in Delhi, they have undertaken significant projects in Pune and are praised for their creative approach and attention to detail.\n\n6. **Architects HCP Design Planning & Management Pvt. Ltd.** - A well-known firm involved in urban design and planning, they have contributed to various significant developments.\n\n7. **Sculptor Architects** - Known for their unique design philosophy and attention to context, they have worked on a variety of project types in Pune.\n\n8. **Pavilion Architecture** - A firm that combines modern design with functionality and has completed various commercial and residential projects in the area.\n\n9. **Design Office** - Focused on contemporary design and user-centric spaces, they have a diverse portfolio, including homes, schools, and public buildings.\n\n10. **Inscape Architects** - Known for their innovative residential and commercial designs, they emphasize sustainable building practices.\n\nIt's advisable to research each architect or firm further, explore their portfolios, and consider client reviews to find the best match for your specific architectural needs.",
